snippet.title: Super Bowling (SNES) Playthrough - NintendoComplete
snippet.description:
A playthrough of American Technos' 1992 Super NES arcade-style bowling game, Super Bowling. 

Played a game of Turkey Bowl, scored 208.

Even though it's a totally different game, does this feel a lot like the awesome Neo Geo League Bowling to anybody else?

______
No cheats were used during the recording of this video.
